  "title": "EVENTS AND MARKETING (🌟NO DESK!! ALL VIBES🌟)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Ditch the Desk. Join the Action. 🚨</strong></h2><p>Feeling stuck in a routine? Wanna break free from the 9–5 drag and do something exciting <em>with purpose</em>? At<strong> AXISREACH Organisation</strong>, we’re shaking up the scene with face-to-face marketing that makes brands stand out—and we want YOU on board.<br /></p><p>🎯 <strong>What You’ll Be Up To:</strong></p><ul><li>Be the face of big-name brands at events and roadshows</li><li>Connect with people, create vibes, and make marketing <em>fun</em></li><li>Lead with confidence and keep the energy flowing on-site</li></ul><p>🌟 <strong>What’s In It For You:</strong></p><ul><li>💬 <strong>1-on-1 Coaching</strong>: Learn the ropes from day one—no experience needed!</li><li>🌏 <strong>Travel Perks</strong>: Regional training + exposure = serious level-up</li><li>🥳 <strong>Team Culture</strong>: We’re talking squad goals—supportive, fun, and full of laughs</li><li>🚀 <strong>Career Growth</strong>: Clear path to leadership, and we’re not just saying that</li></ul><p>👀 <strong>You’ll Love This Role If You’re:</strong></p><ul><li>A people person who loves making new connections</li><li>Hungry to learn, grow, and glow ✨</li><li>Positive vibes only and not afraid to take on new challenges</li></ul><p>🎉 <strong>Ready to do something different (and awesome)?</strong><br /><strong>Apply now</strong> and let’s build a career that actually excites you.</p>",
